T02TD1641E:268b-0: @268b # // s'atstsha gdab pa'i man ngag la dang po 'jim pa byas nas mdun du bzhag ste /
T02TD1641E:268b-1: rang nyid lhag pa'i lhar bsams la /
T02TD1641E:268b-2: tshad med pa bzhi bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1641E:268b-3: de nas chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i sngags kyis 'jim pa mi dmigs par bsgoms la /
T02TD1641E:268b-4: cho ga gsum gyis he ru ka yab yum gyi skur bskyed do //
T02TD1641E:268b-5: de nas snying ga'i hr'i:'am h'um gi 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bkug la //
T02TD1641E:268b-6: he ru ka yab yum la bstim par bya /
T02TD1641E:268b-7: de nas yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa las 'od du zhu ste /
T02TD1641E:268b-8: byang chub kyi sems su gnas pa las he ru ka'i snying po nyi shu rtsa gcig gis byin gyis brlabs te /
T02TD1641E:268b-9: yang de nyid kyis gdab par bya'o //
T02TD1641E:269a-1: ru ka re re bsams la /
T02TD1641E:269a-2: de re re las he ru ka mang po spro ba dang /
T02TD1641E:269a-4: bdag dang gzhan gyi don rdzogs par bsam mo //
T02TD1641E:269a-5: de nas rten 'brel gyi sngags kyis mjug bsdu'o//
